\pard\intbl\ql
{{\b
Aims of the course: }}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{The aim of this course is to teach the students use marketing tools 
in the area of business, especially in retail companies\'2e Methods 
used when gaining information through market research are emphasised\'2e 
Price and price survey, especially from the point of view of the consumer, 
are given attention when talking about marketing mix\'2e With respect 
for the trends in communication, the issue of in\_store marketing 
is stressed in the course\'2e \line
}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{\~}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{{\b
Learning outcomes and competences: }}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{Upon successful completion of this course, students will be able to: 
\line
\_ use marketing tools in the area of business focused mainly on retail 
companies, \line
\_ use particular methods of market research to gain information needed 
to use marketing tools, \line
\_ prepare a survey of brand awareness using aided awareness and top 
of mind awareness methods, \line
\_ prepare a price survey with the aim to find out the expected price, 
test the price scale and set a price threshold, \line
\_ apply particular methods of qualitative market research \line
\_ propose a marketing strategy for retail company or for its business 
operation unit\'2e \line
 \line
}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{\~}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
